---
// Brand logos — real marks from Simple Icons (CC0) + Lobe Icons (MIT).
// Rendered as currentColor on the warm-light palette.
// AutoGen + Mastra do not have official open-source SVGs in either
// registry, so they're mentioned in the eyebrow line instead of the row.
---
<section class="logo-wall">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="lw-eyebrow">Works with the agents you already ship — incl. LangGraph, AutoGen, Mastra</p>
